jvm.usage-rate
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.jvm.total.used', filter=filter('spark_process', 'master')).sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('gauge.jvm.total.committed', filter=filter('spark_process', 'master')).sum().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B).publish(label='C')

chart.name: jvm.usage-rate
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.jvm.total.used', filter=filter('spark_process', 'worker')).mean(by=['worker_port']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('gauge.jvm.total.committed', filter=filter('spark_process', 'worker')).mean(by=['worker_port']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B).publish(label='C')
